View files and Nano Editor

Displaying the contents of files

Cat File   ->Display the contents of file
more file  ->Browse through a text file
less file  ->More features than more
head file  ->Output the begginning (or top) portion of file
tail file -> Output the ending (or bottom) portion of file. Display only 10 lines by default.Change this behaviour with -n 
n=number of lines
tail- 15 files.txt
tail -f file follow the file
Display data as it is being written to the file


Nano Editor
Simple editor
Easy to learn
Not advanced and vi or emacs
Use pico instead
Save file ctrl o and press enter




